---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 249
  - Title: Qur’ân
    Location: I 48
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Judgement=No Helping Friend That Day
---
And guard yourselves against a day when no soul will in aught avail
another, nor will intercession be accepted from it, nor will
compensation be received from it, nor will they be helped.
